Bitcoin Server (bs) is a console application that is included as part of [[libbitcoin-server|Libbitcoin_Server]]. It implements a full node on the Bitcoin P2P network as well as a blockchain query service based on  (1.1).

Documentation (1.2) and signed binaries (1.3) for Linux, OSX and Windows are available on GitHub.

